y, our self-supervised U-Net performs better than five\nsegmentation models which were trained in supervised manner on the\nKvasir-Sessile dataset.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 17 Oct 2021 09:31:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-19"}
