e beams foreseen during LHC Run 3 (2022-2025) of 539 MJ per\nbeam. In this paper an integral overview of the operational behaviour of the\ndumps and the upgraded configurations are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 17 Oct 2021 10:24:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 Oct 2021 12:08:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-17"}
